trans-unit.source: Extends design-time behavior for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml" /> Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Extiende el comportamiento en tiempo de diseño para el control de servidor web <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Xml" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <see langword="false" /> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: Es <see langword="true" /> para liberar tanto recursos administrados como no administrados; es <see langword="false" /> para liberar únicamente recursos no administrados.

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are used by the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner" /> control and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Libera los recursos no administrados utilizados por el control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner" /> y, de forma opcional, libera los recursos administrados.

trans-unit.source: Call <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A> when you are finished using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> class.
trans-unit.target: Llame a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A> cuando haya terminado con el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> clase.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A> method leaves the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: El método <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A> deja el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> en un estado no utilizable.

trans-unit.source: After calling <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A>, you must release all references to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Después de llamar a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A>, debe liberar todas las referencias a la <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> para que el recolector de elementos no utilizados pueda reclamar la memoria que el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> estaba ocupando.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información, consulte [limpiar recursos no administrados](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/unmanaged.md) y [implementa un método Dispose](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md).

trans-unit.source: Always call <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A> before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Realice siempre una llamada a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A> antes de liberar la última referencia al objeto <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner>.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: En caso contrario, los recursos que está usando no se liberarán hasta que el recolector de elementos no utilizados llame al método <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> del objeto `Finalize`.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A> method is called by the public `Dispose()` method and the <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A> público llama el método `Dispose()` método y <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose()` invokes the protected `Dispose(Boolean)` method with `disposing` set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: El `Dispose()` invoca el protegido `Dispose(Boolean)` método con `disposing` establecido en `true`.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invokes `Dispose` with `disposing` set to `false`.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Object.Finalize%2A> invoca `Dispose` con `disposing` establecido en `false`.

trans-unit.source: When `disposing` is `true`, the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A> method releases all resources that are held by any managed objects that this <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> references.
trans-unit.target: Cuando `disposing` es `true`, <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A> método libera todos los recursos retenidos por los objetos administrados que este <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner> referencias.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A> method invokes the `Dispose()` method of each referenced object.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.XmlDesigner.Dispose%2A> método invoca el `Dispose()` método de cada objeto que se hace referencia.

trans-unit.source: When overriding <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, because the <see langword="Dispose" /> method can be called multiple times by other objects, be careful not to reference objects that have been previously disposed of in an earlier call to the <see langword="Dispose" /> method.
trans-unit.target: Al reemplazar <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, porque la <see langword="Dispose" /> método puede recibir varias llamadas de otros objetos, tenga cuidado de no hacer referencia a objetos que se hayan eliminado en una llamada anterior a la <see langword="Dispose" /> método.

trans-unit.source: For more information about how to implement <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, see [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md)
trans-unit.target: Para obtener más información sobre cómo implementar <see langword="Dispose(Boolean)" />, consulte [implementa un método Dispose](~/docs/standard/garbage-collection/implementing-dispose.md)

trans-unit.source: [Overriding the Finalize Method](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3)
trans-unit.target: [Reemplazar el Finalize (método)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8026cb68-fe93-43fc-96c1-c09ad7d64cd3)

trans-unit.target: Recupera el formato HTML que se usa para representar el control en tiempo de diseño.

trans-unit.target: Obtiene el código HTML utilizado para rellenar un control vacío.

trans-unit.source: The HTML used to fill an empty control.
trans-unit.target: El código HTML utilizado para rellenar un control vacío.

trans-unit.target: Control asociado.

trans-unit.target: Inicializa el diseñador con el control al que está asociada esta instancia del diseñador.
